- What?
- You need me for something. What?

84
00:10:27,102 --> 00:10:29,142
Show him.

85
00:10:47,173 --> 00:10:50,758
At 1030 hours, Wednesday,
a group of government officials

86
00:10:50,845 --> 00:10:53,848
