88
00:10:57,021 --> 00:11:00,724
During the tour, she came into
possession of a top-secret prototype.

89
00:11:00,819 --> 00:11:04,070
Then she boarded
Air Force Three for Lynchburg.

90
00:11:04,157 --> 00:11:06,197
To the American people -

91
00:11:06,285 --> 00:11:11,080
now is the time to rise up and demand
the surrender of the President

92
00:11:11,167 --> 00:11:15,796
and his corrupt theocracy
of lies and terror!

93
00:11:15,883 --> 00:11:19,585
