and on the United States.

103
00:12:01,492 --> 00:12:04,744
Her emergency escape pod
landed somewhere in LA.

104
00:12:04,830 --> 00:12:09,079
Her ELT signal ceased immediately.
After that, silence.

105
00:12:09,170 --> 00:12:11,662
We sent a five-man rescue team.

106
00:12:11,757 --> 00:12:15,377
Within hours of landing
all but one was killed.

107
00:12:15,471 --> 00:12:17,096
Hell of a team.

108
00:12:17,182 --> 00:12:20,433
Skip the commentary, Plissken.

109
00:12:20,520 --> 00:12:22,430
Call me Snake.

110
00:12:22,523 --> 00:12:24,517
Get on with it.

111
00:12:24,609 --> 00:12:26,733
