about your daughter.

144
00:14:15,607 --> 00:14:17,897
Utopia is lost to me.
My daughter is gone.

145
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:22,985
- Last chance, hotshot.
- For what?

146
00:14:23,077 --> 00:14:24,572
Freedom, sir.

147
00:14:24,662 --> 00:14:28,496
