172
00:16:15,160 --> 00:16:17,616
I guess we've got a deal.

173
00:16:24,090 --> 00:16:27,175
Nice to be working with you, hotshot.

174
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:32,382
You'd better hope
I don't make it back.

175
00:16:32,477 --> 00:16:34,387
All of you.

176
00:16:36,191 --> 00:16:38,730
Core burner, magnesium ammo,

177
00:16:38,820 --> 00:16:41,229
500 extra rounds.

178
00:16:41,323 --> 00:16:46,665
Oral projectile. Mouth dart, filled
with urolyde. It will stun the enemy.

179
00:16:46,748 --> 00:16:50,451
