Third World countries.

199
00:19:02,992 --> 00:19:05,662
The Cubans and Brazilians
will invade Miami.

200
00:19:05,746 --> 00:19:10,077
The Colombians are at the border,
we've got a full-scale attack.

201
00:19:10,169 --> 00:19:13,125
- High stakes.
- How am I going in?

202
00:19:13,215 --> 00:19:17,464
Under the San Fernando Sea. Shark
Three submarine, one-man submersible.

203
00:19:17,555 --> 00:19:21,257
Just like the turbine model,
only this one's nuclear-powered.

204
00:19:21,352 --> 00:19:24,640
It's very simple.
Throttle up, throttle back.

205
00:19:24,732 --> 00:19:26,940
Put ashore at the Cuegan Pass.

206
00:19:27,027 --> 00:19:30,030
Go through the mountains
toward the Hollywood Bowl.

207
00:19:30,115 --> 00:19:32,690
Locate the survivor
of the rescue team.

208
00:19:32,786 --> 00:19:34,993
He's your only source of information.

209
00:19:35,081 --> 00:19:37,656
- Do I bring him back?
- Negative.

210
00:19:37,752 --> 00:19:40,707
- Figures.
- He's probably already dead.

211
00:19:40,798 --> 00:19:43,919
Once you go inside,
you're on your own.

212
00:19:44,011 --> 00:19:47,049
Get the black box
back to the submarine.

213
00:19:47,141 --> 00:19:49,929
It's your only way out.
Plissken!

214
00:19:50,688 --> 00:19:53,394
You know what to do with the girl.

215
00:19:53,483 --> 00:19:57,898
We don't need to waste any more time
and money on bullshit trials.

216
00:19:57,990 --> 00:19:59,319
Kill her.

217
00:19:59,409 --> 00:20:01,866
Is that order from the President?

218
00:20:01,954 --> 00:20:05,241
Absolutely. Let's just say
it's best for the country.

219
00:20:05,334 --> 00:20:08,752
By the way,
who gives me the antidote?

220
00:20:08,839 --> 00:20:11,877
- A medical team.
- Neither of you?

221
00:20:11,969 --> 00:20:13,381
- No.
- Good.

222
00:20:16,768 --> 00:20:21,349
Thought you'd try that, hotshot.
The first clip is loaded with blanks.

223
00:20:21,442 --> 00:20:23,269
Bye bye, Snake. Good luck.

224
00:20:28,035 --> 00:20:30,112
Nice and easy now.

225
00:20:46,771 --> 00:20:50,058
- Com check.
- Yeah. I'm here.

226
00:20:50,151 --> 00:20:51,776
Stand by for launch.

227
00:20:51,862 --> 00:20:54,734
Eight hours, eight minutes,
26 seconds

228
00:20:54,824 --> 00:20:56,865
to neurosystem shut-down.

229
00:20:58,997 --> 00:21:01,074
Ignitor.

230
00:21:04,088 --> 00:21:06,545
Fuel rod injection.

231
00:21:09,972 --> 00:21:11,716
She's in the green.

232
00:21:11,808 --> 00:21:15,261
- Lock fuel rods.
- Locked.

233
00:21:15,355 --> 00:21:17,562
Nuclear turbine to 75% power.

234
00:21:24,368 --> 00:21:25,863
75% power.

235
00:21:25,954 --> 00:21:28,161
Hands on switches and counting.

236
00:21:28,249 --> 00:21:29,245
Five...

237
00:21:29,334 --> 00:21:31,244
four... three...

238
00:21:31,337 --> 00:21:33,295
two... one.

239
00:21:33,382 --> 00:21:35,174
Launch.

240
00:22:08,350 --> 00:22:11,970
Watch your speed.
There's lots of obstructions.

241
00:22:20,785 --> 00:22:23,360
His reactor's starting to overheat.

242
00:22:23,456 --> 00:22:26,411
Slow down, you're overloading
the power plant!

243
00:22:26,502 --> 00:22:28,792
You slow down, dickhead.
I'm dying.

244
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:30,921
Plissken!

245
