293
00:30:17,116 --> 00:30:19,525
Did you find the team member?

294
00:30:19,620 --> 00:30:22,576
Yeah, they're using him
for target practice.

295
00:30:22,666 --> 00:30:23,947
What will you do?

296
00:30:24,043 --> 00:30:27,580
Amigos, no matter
where you come from,

297
00:30:27,674 --> 00:30:32,385
